{"tid":1991400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周梓樂、陳彥霖祭壇位置　遭鐵板圍封","createTime":"2020-04-27T11:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T14:57:12.000Z","uid":78546,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d16eb1fc9e4ce2206674ddfcc58f7c25f8a3b55a","tid":1991400,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"去年科大學生周梓樂及知專學生陳彥霖離世，市民在將軍澳尚德停車場設祭壇悼念，連月來祭壇已多次被清拆、破壞。<br />\n<br />\n今日（27日）有工人加裝大型鐵板及雪糕筒圍封地面的祭壇，估計是為了防止市民再設祭壇悼念。記者向其中一名工人了解，他說是受領展指派到場施工。現場的文宣、噴漆全被清除，只剩下一束鮮花放在祭壇附近石壆上，以及一張特首林鄭月娥的相片貼在牆上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3033481920070741/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3033481920070741%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4YICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=126d56d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3033481920070741/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"3da6e53f47324448e7a8156c9e4fafb2c3e9226a","tid":1991400,"uid":326032,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"無牆咪貼板<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyrtMEG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyrtMEG.jpg&h=bdeee487&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df8af952ba95c44d61689b8adce20cece06fa70f","tid":1991400,"uid":16414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3da6e53f47324448e7a8156c9e4fafb2c3e9226a","tid":1991400,"uid":326032,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"無牆咪貼板<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyrtMEG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyrtMEG.jpg&h=bdeee487&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"跟住又整塊板遮住塊板...loop"},{"pid":"022dee89c98bb9210c8902370db6bb0955cdee00","tid"